to article in this month's Bassmaster's magazine.  Have any of you read that article?  If so, what are you thoughts on this very touchy topic.  I personally find no harm in bed fishing as long as the fish is released shortly after catching it.  Such as a quick photograph and weighing.  Now's the time.  What are the Pro's and Con's that I haven't mentioned here?<br>
